Try:
O'Brien, S. J. The Cheetah is Depauperate in Genetic Variation.
Science. 1983
Sorry, I don't have the complete reference here. There are several papers
by O'Brien and his group discussing the lack of genetic variability in
cheetahs and disease, and some on the Florida panther, _Felis concolor
coryi_ and the potential for similar problems.
